  • allocateValueList

    protected abstract List<SmObjectImpl> allocateValueList(ISmObjectData data,
                                   int initialCapacity)
    This method is called in order to allocate a new ArrayList data structure for the dependency when the dependency, being still empty and bound to the EMPTY list, has to be modified. Its role is to allocate a concrete ArrayList for the dependency.
    Parameters:
    data - a model object data
    initialCapacity - a recommended initial capacity for the new ArrayList to allocate
    Returns:
    the allocated list.
